OL,3,CScotland fan in 1,000-mile walk from
OL,4,CHampden to Munich for mental health
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FA football fan is walking 1,000 miles
OL,8,Ffrom Scotland to the Euro 2024
OL,9,Ftournament in Germany to raise money
OL,10,Fand awareness for men's mental health.
OL,12,FCraig Ferguson, 20, of Paisley, will
OL,13,Fwalk from Scotland's national football
OL,14,Fstadium Hampden, in Glasgow, to Munich.
OL,16,FHe will set off at 10am on Saturday
OL,17,Fand will walk for 37 days, with the
OL,18,Faim to arrive in time for the first
OL,19,Fgame of the tournament on June 14
OL,20,Fbetween Germany and Scotland.
