OL,3,CScotland fan in 1,000-mile walk from
OL,4,CHampden to Munich for mental health
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FAll the money he raises will go
OL,8,Ftowards Brothers in Arms, a Scottish
OL,9,Fmen's mental health charity.
OL,11,FMr Ferguson initially intended to
OL,12,Fraise #10,000 but having already
OL,13,Fbeaten that target, he now hopes to
OL,14,Fhit #50,000 by the time he reaches
OL,15,FGermany.
OL,17,FThe first leg of his challenge will
OL,18,Fsee him walk from Glasgow to Hull,
OL,19,FEast Yorkshire, which he hopes to
OL,20,Fcomplete in 12 days.
