OL,4,CHampden to Munich for mental health
OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,FHe will then take the ferry to
OL,8,FRotterdam in Holland, and cross six
OL,9,Fcountries before reaching Germany.
OL,11,FWhile walking, he will wear a
OL,12,Fspecially crafted, ultra-light sports
OL,13,Fkilt in a Euros tartan by Scottish
OL,14,Fkilt-makers Slanj.
OL,16,FThe flags of Scotland's group A
OL,17,Fopponents, Germany, Switzerland and
OL,18,FHungary are all featured in the kilt's
OL,19,Fdesign, while a dark blue backdrop
OL,20,Frepresents the colour of the Scottish
OL,21,Fstrip.
