OL,7,FSupporters can follow his journey
OL,8,Fthrough an online tracker, updated
OL,9,Fdaily using his GPS location.
OL,11,FAhead of his journey, he said: "In the
OL,12,Fsame way that football unites men, I
OL,13,Fhope to unite people and communities
OL,14,Fthroughout my journey across Europe on
OL,15,Fa crucial aspect of wellbeing ` men's
OL,16,Fmental health.
OL,18,F"I am so excited to get going and
OL,19,Fcan't wait to fly the flag for
OL,20,FScotland on this special journey.
