OL,5,Ccharity
OL,7,F"When the going gets tough, I'll
OL,8,Fremind myself why I'm doing it and
OL,9,Fthink of the 12 men that take their
OL,10,Fown lives every single day in the UK.
OL,12,F"It really is a gift to be fit and
OL,13,Fhealthy, and to have the opportunity
OL,14,Fto do something that I love ` to
OL,15,Fexplore new corners of the world and
OL,16,Fto test my fitness.
OL,18,F"Thanks to everyone who has supported
OL,19,Fme thus far, I really do appreciate
OL,20,Fit."
