OL,7,FThe money raised for Brothers in Arms
OL,8,Fwill go towards the development of a
OL,9,Fdigital "talking and listening" tool
OL,10,Fnamed Blethr that aims to lower the
OL,11,Fmale suicide rate in Scotland.
OL,13,FBrothers in Arms founder Dan Proverbs
OL,14,Fthanked Mr Ferguson for his support,
OL,15,Fand said "promoting men's mental
OL,16,Fhealth awareness is a global issue"
OL,17,Fthat is "severely underfunded".
OL,19,FHe added: "We are incredibly proud of
OL,20,FCraig.
